data.description: Welcome to the Pride of Highlands Ranch in the picturesque setting of Chino Valley, Arizona. This stunning, brand-new 2022 home is the epitome of affordable luxury living, complete with all the modern amenities you could desire. Why wait for a new construction when you can make this move-in-ready gem yours today? 1667 E Yorkshire Avenue boasts an inviting open split-floor plan that includes 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a generous 2,262 sqft of living space, all situated on a spacious .22-acre lot with beautifully landscaped grounds. The primary suite is a true retreat, featuring dual vanities, quartz countertops, a luxurious dual-head walk-in shower, a walk-in closet, and convenient backyard access.
